{
  "texts": [
    "These embeddings are numerical representations that encapsulate the semantic content of the passage.",
    "An index is created to store the text passages and their vector embeddings as key-value pairs, which allows for retrieving contextually relevant data efficiently and accurately.",
    "These key-value pairs can be stored in a vector database to avoid re-indexing the documentation each time.",
    "A prompt for the RAG model is indexed using the same embedding model and passed onto the next step in the pipeline.",
    "The querying step uses the vector embedding of the prompt to identify the most relevant passages from the vector database with domain documentation embeddings."
  ]
}